The paper proposes a new algorithm for imitation learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper also discusses issues related to reward bias and sample inefficiency, which are common concerns in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions computer vision (cs.CV) as an application area, and system and control (cs.SY) as a potential area of use.
